nodes.text: Ultimate Sticker Collection: Star Wars is a sticker book in the Ultimate Sticker Collection series from DK Publishing. It contains material previously released in The Ultimate Star Wars Episode I Sticker Book (1999), Ultimate Sticker Book: Star Wars (2004), and Ultimate Sticker Book: Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith (2005).
Ultimate Sticker Collection: Star Wars was first published by DK Publishing on April 2, 2007. A reprint edition was published under the Disney brand in 2015.
